Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  刚才的光是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于见到你了啊  什么感觉？  黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常  H的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个H的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗  H的校长来找你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这身姿实在是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必和我抱在一起游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:00:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校  校长消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要见的是  这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.23,0:01:15.63,up,NTP,0,0,0,,我说大家  在上课啊  安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一回事  不寒而栗的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结城君  你也是  大叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小暗
